{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1170c8295c","title":"对中央转发广东省委关于镇反工作报告的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0e18316040","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"1170c8295c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"9038d9fbb8","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是写在中共中央转发广东省委1956年2月12日关于当前社会镇反工作意见的报告的批语稿上的批语。本篇二是在中央批语福未尾加写的文字。中央于1956年2月29日将广东省委的报告批转上海局、各省市委和自治区党委。"},{"id":"4fcc3ea043","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。瑞卿，即罗瑞卿，当时任公安部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d1eac1615a","type":"title","text":"对中央转发广东省委关于镇反工作报告的批语和修改！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c"},{"id":"9038d9fbb8","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、瑞卿再阅，在尾上加了几句。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c"},{"id":"4fcc3ea043","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东发后，抄公安部可以肯定地说，今年捕人的数目应当较去年大大减少，只捕少数非捕不可的人。杀人的数目无其要少，只系极少数非系不可的人。今年三月底中央公安会议的时候，应当根据新的形势，重新拟订一个计划，报告中央审定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c"},{"id":"1838b9540d","type":"paragraph","text":"1956年2月28日，来访的乘埔塞国王西哈努克亲王为毛泽东佩戴乘埔塞王国的最高勋章。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c"}],"page":{"id":"d9e7521aeb","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"1170c8295c","start":236,"end":237}}}},"__N_SSG":true}